                "content": "\ud83c\udfad Welcome to the Formal Debate!\n\n\ud83d\udccb **Topic**: AI should be regulated\n\n\ud83d\udc65 **Participants and Positions**:\n  \u2022 Pro_001129: For AI regulation\n  \u2022 Con_001129: Against AI regulation\n\n\ud83d\udcdc **Debate Format** (traditional):\n1. Opening Statements - Each participant presents their position\n2. Main Arguments - Each participant makes 3 arguments\n3. Rebuttals - Participants respond to opposing arguments\n4. Closing Statements - Final summaries from each participant\n\n\u2696\ufe0f **Rules**:\n  \u2022 Participants must argue for their assigned position\n\nLet us begin! Pro_001129, please present your opening statement.",
